{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CLLocationDirection","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CLLocationDirection"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"direction"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The value "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0"},{"type":"text","text":" means that the top edge of the map view corresponds to true"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"north. The value "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"90"},{"type":"text","text":" means the top of the map is pointing due east. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"180"},{"type":"text","text":" means the top of the map points due south, and so on."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view immediately. If you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to animate the change, use the "},{"code":"-setDirection:animated:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method instead."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The heading of the map, measured in degrees clockwise from true north.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/direction"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/direction"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"direction","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/ma